Chromosome number
:—2n = 18 (Krishnappa & Reshme 1982); n = 9 (
Hans 1973
); 2n = 19 (
Hsu 1967
); 2n = 20 (
Chopde 1965
).

Ecology :—Accidentally dispersed by humans as contaminant; globally considered as weed of cereals, orchards and plantations. The species occurs in disturbed areas, often near salt water (
Steinmann et al. 2016
).

Alien status :—Neophyte native to the New World, recorded by mistake in Italy (
Galasso et al. 2018b
).

